videos.headline: South Carolina's offense dominates UNC in Mayo Bowl
videos.description: Gamecocks' offense unleashes with trick plays and TE Jaheim Bell's two touchdowns and 159 receiving yards in the 38-21 win over North Carolina in Duke's Mayo Bowl.
